          "text": "不背么，也好。与我讲来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江花右",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是，我讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江花右",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我。不不……讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！你这丫头，今日为何颠三倒四，敢是疯了不成？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（百花公主剑鞘击桌，惊起海俊。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀唬！唬得我魂飞胆摇，"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望恕却残生这遭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "披肝胆敢装奸狡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亦非是越墙之盗"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亦非是挟匕的那英豪"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "觑他容貌非奸狡，"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俊堂堂一貌丰标。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亦非是越墙之盗"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亦非是挟匕的那英豪"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亦非是越墙之盗"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亦非是挟匕的那英豪"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既不是越墙之盗，"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "因甚事潜身来到？"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少时刻一命难逃！"
        },
        {
          "character": "将此事诉根苗、江花右",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！那一汉子，家住哪里？姓甚名谁？快快讲来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是，是，是。公主容禀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恨无端生出祸根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "𠲔！可恨那叭喇呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔！你是甚等样人，敢言我内侍叭喇？"
        },
        {
          "character": "江花右",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是啊！你是甚等样人，敢言我内侍叭喇？"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是，是，是。哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他忌才能暗藏机巧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小生海俊，新任西府参军。不想内侍叭喇，假意庆贺为由，将酒把我灌醉呵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知怎么到了公主内庭，内庭上来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀公主呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恕微臣误入在蓬岛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔！你深夜潜入内庭，理当问斩，念你中了他人之计，我就不杀你了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江花右",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快谢了公主！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是，是，是。多谢公主！"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只是便宜了你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江花右！"
        },
        {
          "character": "江花右",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看看哪里粉墙可越，送他出去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江花右",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀且住！我看公主倒有爱我哥哥之意，唔，我自有道理。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "江花右",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闭门推出窗前月……"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊妹子，你送我出去呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "江花右",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "江花右",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吩咐梅花自主张。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（江花右下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你还未曾去么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未曾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江花右呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知去向。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我唤来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊江花右！江花右！这丫头不知往哪里去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊海生，深夜无人，待我送你出去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢公主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就在此攀梅而过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳公主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "海生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休将老梅来折损，待他乘月泄春光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？那公主为何道此两句？唔，莫非她有爱我之意呀？唔，我且闪过一旁，听"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她讲些什么。有理吓有理！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖起三更鼓〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那海生，言语清朗，气度轩昂。我有意将终身托付与他，怎奈女孩儿家，羞"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人答答，不好启齿。吖有了！待我稟过父王，方好成其美事。啊呀……好个海"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "生！好个海生！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "海生在！"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（雁儿落） 广寒岑寂，仙子思飘遥，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "须知道桂蕊向少年抛。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖雅笛〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "海生，我不杀你，你心中可明白？"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多蒙公主将终身相许，我是何以为报？何……以为报？"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只恐书生情薄，后来忘恩负义！"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！我若负了公主之情，对天可表。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但凭……"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（雁儿落） 明月在上，照我心苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我岂做王魁把盟山负却了？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖起四更鼓〗。海俊逼百花公主，跪步至上场口。〖曲牌收〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "百花公主 （雁儿落） 啊呀海生呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何必心急怎的？心急怎的？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀海生呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "纵使欢娱，怎免得旁人嘲笑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多蒙公主见爱，必须赠我一物，以为今日定情之证。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这……"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唵……"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有宝剑二股。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喔！"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今赠一股与君。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔！"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "以为定情之证。"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，多谢公主！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "百花公主 （同雁儿落） 相逢好，赠青锋为表照。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好姻缘于飞及早。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待功成渡鹊桥。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（江花右上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "江花右",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？公主叫你出去，你为何不出去呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……"
        },
        {
          "character": "江花右",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢公主不杀与他，还赠送宝剑，我这里当面谢过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？你是他的什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "江花右",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是他的……"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "江花右",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹子呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吖，原来你们是兄妹？"
        },
        {
          "character": "海俊、江花右",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
